        CAMPUS FOOD PASS SCANNER SYSTEM
========================================================

PROJECT TYPE:
Real-Time Java Project Using Set Interface + DSA

========================================================
                    PROJECT STORY
========================================================

A large university is conducting a Tech Fest.

Thousands of students visit the food court daily.

Each student receives a unique Food Pass ID.

RULES:
1. A student can eat only once
2. Duplicate entries must be blocked
3. VIP students get special access
4. Security monitors fraud attempts
5. Admin wants crowd analytics

Students must build the system using:
- Java Set Interface
- Exception Handling
- DSA Concepts

