3. Custom Exceptions
4. File Handling
5. Menu Driven Program
6. Comparable & Comparator

========================================================
                    MODULE 1
             STUDENT ENTRY SCANNER
========================================================

OBJECTIVE:
-----------
Prevent duplicate food entries.

DATA STRUCTURE:
----------------
HashSet<String>

WHY HASHSET?
--------------
1. No duplicate values
2. Fast searching
3. O(1) average lookup time

REAL-TIME FLOW:
----------------

Scan Student ID
        |
        V
Check in HashSet
        |
  ----------------
  |              |
NO             YES
  |              |
Allow Entry    Duplicate Entry

EXAMPLE:
---------

Input:
S101
S102
S103
S101

Output:
S101 Entry Allowed
S102 Entry Allowed
S103 Entry Allowed
S101 Duplicate Entry Detected

