========================================================
                    MODULE 4
                FRAUD DETECTION
========================================================

DSA CONCEPT:
-------------
Sliding Window

STORY:
-------
Security suspects repeated duplicate scans
within short time periods.

TASK:
------
Find maximum duplicate attempts within
window size K.

EXAMPLE:
---------

Entries:
S1 S2 S1 S3 S1 S2 S2

K = 4

WINDOWS:
---------

Window 1:
S1 S2 S1 S3

Window 2:
S2 S1 S3 S1

Window 3:
S1 S3 S1 S2

Window 4:
S3 S1 S2 S2

LEARNING:
-----------
1. Fixed Size Window
2. Frequency Map
3. Optimization
4. Real-Time Monitoring

